treeComm_occ_hclust <- treeComm_occ %>%
    vegdist(method = "bray") %>%
    hclust(method = "ward.D2")

treeComm_occ_dendro <- treeComm_occ_hclust %>%
    as.dendrogram() %>%
    color_labels(col = col_plotType[
        match(treeComm_occ_hclust$labels, plots$plotID)
    ][treeComm_occ_hclust$order])

                  "wet"),

Forest structure and diversity

plots <- plots %>%
    left_join(
        data.frame(stemDensity = rowSums(treeComm_stem),
                   totBasalArea = rowSums(treeComm_basalArea)/400,
                   D0 = specnumber(treeComm_stem),
                   D1 = exp(diversity(treeComm_stem, index = "shannon")),
                   D2 = diversity(treeComm_stem, index = "invsimpson")) %>%
            rownames_to_column(var = "plotID"),
        by = "plotID") %>%
    left_join(data.frame(cluster = treeComm_stem_clusters) %>%
                  rownames_to_column(var = "plotID"),
              by = "plotID")

fun_se <- function(x) sd(x)/sqrt(length(x))

plots_summary <- plots %>%
    filter(!is.na(cluster)) %>%
    group_by(cluster) %>%
    summarise(stemDensity_mean = mean(stemDensity),
              stemDensity_se = fun_se(stemDensity),
              totBasalArea_mean = mean(totBasalArea),
              totBasalArea_se = fun_se(totBasalArea),
              D0_mean = mean(D0),
              D0_se = fun_se(D0),
              D1_mean = mean(D1),
              D1_se = fun_se(D1),
              D2_mean = mean(D2),
              D2_se = fun_se(D2)) %>%
    mutate(cluster = as.factor(cluster)) %>%
    mutate(cluster = factor(cluster, levels = c(2,1,3,4)))

ggplot(plots_summary %>%
           pivot_longer(cols = -cluster) %>%
           separate(name, into = c("var", "stat")) %>%
           pivot_wider(names_from = stat, values_from = value),
       aes(x = cluster, fill = cluster)) +
    geom_col(aes(y = mean)) +
    geom_segment(aes(xend = cluster, y = mean - se, yend = mean + se)) +
    facet_wrap(~var, scales = "free_y") +
    scale_fill_manual(
        name = "Cluster & interpretation",
        labels = c("2 - Secondary forest (exotic-dominated)",
                   "1 - Secondary forest (native-dominated)",
                   "3 - Primary (non-swamp)",
                   "4 - Primary (freshwater swamp)"),
        values = c("purple", "palegreen", "darkgreen", "blue")
        ) +
    labs(x = "", y = "") +
    theme_classic()

Tree floristics

By stem counts

treeComm_stem_floristics <- treeComm_stem %>%
    as.data.frame() %>%
    rownames_to_column(var = "plotID") %>%
    left_join(plots %>% select(plotID, cluster),
              by = "plotID") %>%
    select(-plotID) %>%
    group_by(cluster) %>%
    summarise_all(function(x) sum(x)/length(x)/(0.04))

Digging deeper into Group 1

cluster1_plotIDS <- plots %>%
    filter(cluster == 1,
           type_FT != "wet",
           type_FT != "E") %>%
    pull(plotID)

cluster1_treeComm <- treeComm_stem[rownames(treeComm_stem) %in% cluster1_plotIDS,] %>%
    select_if(colSums(.)>0)

cluster1_treeComm_hclust <- cluster1_treeComm %>%
    vegdist(method = "bray") %>%
    hclust(method = "ward.D2")

cluster1_treeComm_dendro <- cluster1_treeComm_hclust %>%
    as.dendrogram() %>%
    color_labels(col = col_plotType[
        match(cluster1_treeComm_hclust$labels, plots$plotID)
    ][cluster1_treeComm_hclust$order])

labels_cex(cluster1_treeComm_dendro) <- 0.5

cluster1_treeComm_clusters <- cutree(cluster1_treeComm_hclust, k = 2)

plot(cluster1_treeComm_dendro);
rect.dendrogram(cluster1_treeComm_dendro,
                k = 2,
                lower_rect = -0.08)

cluster1_treeComm_clusters_isa <- indicspecies::multipatt(
    cluster1_treeComm, cluster1_treeComm_clusters
)

summary(cluster1_treeComm_clusters_isa)
